{"tid":581152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"范徐麗泰 : 贊成廢除兩屆的限制  國家要有一個強而有力的領導","createTime":"2018-03-05T05:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T10:06:46.000Z","uid":188,"like":2,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"60072c5477f58cc39215838c9f3bf24c812b6934","tid":581152,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T05:52:49.000Z","msg":"全國人大會議開幕，總理李克強在政府工作報告中，繼2014年後再次無提及「港人治港」、「高度自治」等字眼。 列席會議的前全國人大常委范徐麗泰在會後表示，「一國兩制」、「港人治港」、「高度自治」是國策，絕對不會因為香港有人推動「港獨」而改變。 她又認為，未來更加應該彰顯憲法和基本法的權威，但這並不代表中央收緊對港政策，而是有人存心誤解或誤導市民對國策、憲法、基本法的理解，因此有必要提升港人對憲法和基本法的認知。至於有關做法是「鬆」還是「緊」就是個人看法。 范徐麗泰又說，贊成在憲法中刪除國家主席不能連任超過兩屆的限制，但這與「終身制」無關。她說，國家要向前發展就必須要有一個強而有力的領導。 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/135242_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F135242_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg&h=7f69d3d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d622033d3ba02051b4b757d90441336be3c6308c","tid":581152,"uid":188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T05:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd9d49ba434852159aa412333910ea28d5aa643","tid":581152,"uid":188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T05:54:38.000Z","msg":"人唔笑"},{"pid":"9643c1a06b2ea4600047bb1d31444e4374c8b757","tid":581152,"uid":137063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T05:55:35.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"3b2bc83fe8bf772d887073f6fa1ccd15daee353c","tid":581152,"uid":188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T05:57:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但這與「終身制」無關</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7485c195cbca60fa8c90324ce8fc4